* A helper class to map a zone name to metazone and back to the * appropriate zone id for the particular locale. *

* The zid<->metazone mappings are based on CLDR metaZones.xml. * The alias mappings are based on Link entries in tzdb data files and * CLDR's supplementalMetadata.xml.

methods.name: public static String toZid(String zid, Locale locale)
public static String getSystemCanonicalID(String zid)
